cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.MS, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a control synthesis algorithm based on temporal logic specifications. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses controller synthesis for dynamical systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper proposes a novel encoding using binary decision diagrams. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is another possible category as the paper discusses benchmark results and implementation of the proposed ideas on a prototype tool. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with automated control synthesis.
